description: Available in both small (5mm) and large (9mm) sizes these little studs are a perfect example of simplicity at its finest. description: These small little hoops have the perfect blend of edge and glam! The small studded spikes and alternating crystal accents create an amazingly adorable combination. description: This ring is a simple 5mm band available in Gold or Rose Gold. The Gold ring is available with crystal detailing and the Rose Gold rings are available both with or without the crystals. Quality fashion forward pieces perfect for any girl!

Made of stainless steel these pieces will not tarnish or discolor with normal wear. They are made to last!

description:
These beautiful bracelets have roman numerals embossed onto the surface to create a unique and interesting design. Available in both Gold and Rose Gold they are sure to be a great addition to anyone's wardrobe! 

All our pieces are made of stainless steel and will not tarnish or discolor with normal wear. These pieces are made to last and would compliment anyone's style.

Available in both gold and silver, these bracelets are edgy! Studded with small spikes around the circumference, this bracelet will add a little bit of edge to any outfit. Opening on a hinge, it is easy to wear!

Made of stainless steel this bracelet will not tarnish or discolor with normal wear! It is made to last!

description:
These beautiful bracelets are inspired by the Cartier Love bracelets. Designed to give you the same chic style for a fraction of the price, they are perfect for the fashion forward girl on a budget! These bracelets and all our other pieces will add glamour and style to any outfit. 

All our pieces are made of stainless steel and so they will not tarnish or discolor with normal wear. We have these available in Rose Gold (with a screw closure, like the original) or in silver (with a hinge closure). We will soon be restocking Yellow Gold so please check back with us often!

name: Cartier Inspired "Juste un Clou" Bracelets
description:
These beautiful pieces are inspired by the Cartier "Juste un Clou" bracelets. Shaped like a nail that opens on a hinge these bracelets are very chic! These are perfect for a fashionista on a budget! 

All our pieces are made of stainless steel and will not tarnish or discolor with normal wear. These are made to last! Available in Gold, Rose Gold, or Silver these pieces are ready to accessorize any outfit!

description: This small little pendant is simply perfect. A small caged tube delicately hangs from a 16" chain and would be the perfect accent any day.
